            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指升165點報26750點 龍旗科技首掛高開12.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段跟隨外圍向好，恒生指數開市報26750點，升165點或0.62%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5795點，升48點或0.85%；國企指數以9173點開市，升50點或0.55%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報166元，升1.72%；騰訊(00700)開報604.5元，升0.33%。滙控(00005)開報129.1元，升0.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南山鋁業(02610)折讓6.39%配股，該股今早開報66.25元，跌3.85%。鈞達(02865)折讓1.08%配股，該股今早則升0.81%，報22.42元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍旗科技(09611)今早登場，以35元開市，較招股價31元高12.9%。</p>\n</div>",
